. Finalize payment to guarantee it.","copy_code":"Copiar chave (Pix Copia e Cola)","hide_qr_code":"Hide QR code","pay_steps":{"0":"Abra o aplicativo do seu banco e acesse a área Pix","1":"Selecione a opção pagar com código Pix Copia e Cola e cole o código no espaço indicado no aplicativo","2":"Após o pagamento, você receberá por email as informações de acesso à sua compra"},"qr_code_will_be_generated":"We\'ve received your order and it is being processed in the system. As soon as your QR code is generated, you will receive an email at {0} with payment instructions.","show_qr_code":"Mostrar QR code"},"product_total_value":"Total price of the Product","purchase_approved":"your purchase has been approved :)","purchase_being_analyzed":"Your payment is \\"Under analysis\\". Check your email to keep track of your purchase. ","purchase_detail":"Order details","purchase_pending":"Now, you just need to finish the payment","purchase_registered":"Your purchase has been registered","seller_contact":"Write down the contact details of the service provider:","start_learning":"Start learning","transaction_code":"Transaction code:","watch_your_mail_spam":"In some cases, your email service might mistakenly send our emails to the SPAM folder. We recommend you check your SPAM folder once payment is approved - the access details for your product might be there!"},"ticket":{"booking_expired_description":"Please, refresh this page.<br /> You will continue to buy the same ticket. ","booking_expired_title":"Your reservation has expired!","non_transferable":"Tickets are non-transferable after validation.","reservation_expires_in":"Your reservation expires in","reservation_time":"Reservation time","ticket_data_reference":"Information for Participant nº {0}","ticket_information":"Information about your ticket"}}')},,,,,,,,,function(e,t,n){"use strict";var r=n(9),o=(n(63),n(4),n(95),n(0)),l=n(1),c=window.__NUXT__;function d(){if(!this._hydrated)return this.$fetch()}function f(){if((e=this).$vno